WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
笙ｪThat day笙ｪ

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
笙ｪNothing stays together forever笙ｪ

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
笙ｪI've quit romance笙ｪ

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
笙ｪWho hasn't failed again笙ｪ

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
笙ｪCrying in death笙ｪ

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
笙ｪAnd in life笙ｪ

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
笙ｪEven now笙ｪ

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
笙ｪWe keep learning笙ｪ

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
笙ｪIt's no surprise笙ｪ

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
笙ｪBeing happy is so hard笙ｪ

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
笙ｪWeirdly, I became a role model笙ｪ

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
笙ｪOn the day we met again, we said hi笙ｪ

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
笙ｪIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaint笙ｪ

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
笙ｪWho can do anything without regret笙ｪ

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
笙ｪI am all right笙ｪ

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
笙ｪMay you live in peace笙ｪ

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
笙ｪLet the world roar笙ｪ

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
笙ｪSounds like a carnival笙ｪ

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
笙ｪBeing alive is never dull笙ｪ

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
笙ｪHow wonderful to be free笙ｪ

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
笙ｪI became even better without you笙ｪ

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
笙ｪNothing can be perfect笙ｪ

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
笙ｪWe bless each other in pain笙ｪ

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
笙ｪWe nod and smile笙ｪ

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
笙ｪMay we both be well笙ｪ

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.040 --> 01:43.952
=Episode 14=

02:02.794 --> 02:03.314
Welcome back.

02:10.034 --> 02:11.714
The soup will be ready soon.

02:15.395 --> 02:18.075
Fang Lei picked up Haochen
after school today.

02:23.955 --> 02:25.034
She told me

02:25.154 --> 02:26.795
that Shen Haochen is your son.

02:32.355 --> 02:33.395
Is this true?

02:54.154 --> 02:54.675
Yes.

02:56.474 --> 02:57.795
He's my illegitimate son.

03:00.434 --> 03:01.795
Why did you hide this from me?

03:02.314 --> 03:03.434
Didn't I tell you

03:03.474 --> 03:05.434
that do not say anything

03:05.434 --> 03:06.675
affecting our relationship?

03:06.714 --> 03:08.115
When do you want to tell me?

03:08.754 --> 03:09.675
Never?

03:11.995 --> 03:13.314
I always thought

03:15.034 --> 03:17.235
you loved and understood me,

03:19.275 --> 03:21.154
so you've silently supported me

03:21.154 --> 03:22.474
in pursuing my career.

03:22.795 --> 03:24.314
Only today did I realize

03:25.275 --> 03:26.634
that you just wanted to use me

03:26.634 --> 03:27.634
and my career

03:27.634 --> 03:29.594
as your tools.

03:30.235 --> 03:31.075
You just want to use

03:31.075 --> 03:34.355
my profession to win over Jiang Yun

03:34.955 --> 03:36.515
and every business partner

03:36.515 --> 03:37.995
you needed for your career.

03:39.955 --> 03:41.594
You're just trying to use me.

03:42.675 --> 03:43.714
But I don't understand.

03:46.194 --> 03:47.634
Why did you lie to me?

04:10.515 --> 04:11.754
Speaking of it,

04:12.434 --> 04:13.795
you're in no position

04:14.395 --> 04:17.074
(Xu Yan's Profile)
to question me.

04:31.115 --> 04:32.235
When I first met you,

04:34.434 --> 04:36.155
you possess the charm I like.

04:37.475 --> 04:39.035
You are interesting enough.

04:42.155 --> 04:43.715
My mom is extremely particular,

04:43.795 --> 04:45.754
and few women could win her favor,

04:46.394 --> 04:47.475
but you could.

04:47.555 --> 04:48.595
You get along with her.

04:49.394 --> 04:51.035
I prefer smart women.

04:52.915 --> 04:53.555
Second,

04:53.874 --> 04:55.434
you have the qualities I admire

04:56.035 --> 04:57.074
and the ability to endure.

04:58.954 --> 04:59.834
If I find a woman

04:59.834 --> 05:01.514
from a prestigious background,

05:04.235 --> 05:05.834
they might not tolerate

05:06.314 --> 05:07.874
the mistakes of my youth

05:09.634 --> 05:11.035
or accept my son.

05:15.274 --> 05:19.155
You look like a proper noble lady,

05:19.194 --> 05:21.074
but without their arrogance

05:21.874 --> 05:23.595
and unpleasant temper.

05:25.595 --> 05:26.355
Third,

05:27.434 --> 05:28.394
your ambition.

05:30.314 --> 05:31.074
From the start,

05:31.074 --> 05:32.634
you wanted to host a Family Feast,

05:32.795 --> 05:34.035
and then you aimed

05:34.035 --> 05:36.715
to be a news anchor.

05:41.115 --> 05:42.595
It actually benefits my career.

05:43.475 --> 05:44.394
Yes, I lied to you.

05:45.274 --> 05:46.874
But didn't I generously provide

05:46.874 --> 05:48.194
full support to you?

05:54.355 --> 05:55.274
Lin Tao.

05:57.274 --> 05:58.115
(I put pressure)

05:58.115 --> 05:59.995
(on the bank where he was working.)

06:01.954 --> 06:02.795
Zhou Zeyuan.

06:04.274 --> 06:06.274
He blackmailed and threatened you.

06:10.915 --> 06:12.795
When he was at his wit's end,

06:12.834 --> 06:14.035
I gave him funding.

06:14.274 --> 06:16.595
When a gambler is at his wit's end,

06:16.595 --> 06:17.715
he won't turn back.

06:18.035 --> 06:19.355
He would only take a big gamble.

06:19.555 --> 06:21.595
Then, I put him to prison.

06:21.795 --> 06:23.355
Zhou Zeyuan was arrested.

06:29.355 --> 06:30.715
Because I lied to you,

06:31.675 --> 06:33.434
I'm willing to spend money

06:34.155 --> 06:35.834
to maintain your lies unrevealed.

06:36.475 --> 06:37.915
All you need to do

06:38.355 --> 06:39.834
is being a perfect wife

06:39.874 --> 06:41.194
with a respectable job,

06:41.274 --> 06:42.834
keeping my family pleased.

06:42.995 --> 06:43.634
And me?

06:43.834 --> 06:44.954
As your husband,

06:45.314 --> 06:46.634
I'll fulfill my duty

06:47.314 --> 06:48.514
to boost your career.

06:51.314 --> 06:53.155
Stop looking at me so pitifully.

06:53.874 --> 06:55.514
Didn't you approach me

06:56.194 --> 06:57.475
with ulterior motives?

06:58.795 --> 07:00.074
You tried every mean

07:00.274 --> 07:01.595
to become my wife,

07:01.715 --> 07:03.595
just wanting my wealth, my connections

07:03.675 --> 07:04.795
and all my resources.

07:06.194 --> 07:08.634
You used me to build your credibility,

07:09.155 --> 07:10.475
winning the public trust.

07:10.754 --> 07:12.555
Do you think this is absolutely safe?

07:13.155 --> 07:14.834
They come back to me
once you turn around.

07:16.194 --> 07:17.394
My generosity

07:17.995 --> 07:19.434
made your sweet dreams come true.

07:19.434 --> 07:20.274
Do you know that?

07:23.675 --> 07:25.514
So everything you did to me

07:25.514 --> 07:26.475
was all lies.

07:29.834 --> 07:31.155
I just have one question.

07:36.274 --> 07:37.074
Have you ever...

07:44.874 --> 07:46.475
Have you ever truly loved me?

07:48.874 --> 07:50.954
From the moment I knew you were a fraud,

07:53.915 --> 07:55.355
I would never fall in love with you.

08:01.675 --> 08:02.795
I lied to you too.

08:05.035 --> 08:06.074
I didn't expect you

08:06.115 --> 08:07.074
to genuinely love me.

08:08.475 --> 08:09.715
Just take what we need.

08:23.434 --> 08:24.314
I understand now.

08:32.554 --> 08:34.634
I finally understand everything now.

08:38.315 --> 08:39.315
So,

08:42.235 --> 08:43.914
when I made your mom happy,

08:46.715 --> 08:48.154
when I treated Haochen well,

08:50.674 --> 08:52.394
when I pleased you,

08:52.394 --> 08:55.195
I thought those watches,
cars, and jewelry you gave me

08:57.514 --> 08:59.315
were out of love.

09:04.034 --> 09:05.034
But to you,

09:08.195 --> 09:09.554
they were just bonus to me, right?

09:12.475 --> 09:15.355
It's kind of my recognition to you

09:15.794 --> 09:17.514
for meeting my standards.

09:22.715 --> 09:23.394
Xu Yan.

09:24.914 --> 09:25.995
If you dwell on this,

09:27.435 --> 09:28.835
it would make you look foolish.

09:37.194 --> 09:42.221
笙ｪWhen I melt into the crowd笙ｪ

09:45.435 --> 09:46.235
(In this world,)

09:46.235 --> 09:47.394
(there's no perfect choice.)

09:48.674 --> 09:49.514
(You have to know)

09:49.514 --> 09:50.595
(the choices you make)

09:51.315 --> 09:53.394
(and the price should be paid.)

09:54.512 --> 09:58.723
笙ｪTo the corner where I sheltered
from rain and tears笙ｪ

09:58.992 --> 10:05.828
笙ｪOnly then did I realize
what I had was precious笙ｪ

10:06.160 --> 10:13.099
笙ｪMisplaced glory is just danger's omen笙ｪ

10:13.712 --> 10:17.808
笙ｪWhen city lights light,
but there's nowhere to turn to笙ｪ

10:18.000 --> 10:21.199
笙ｪHow should I compromise?笙ｪ

10:21.456 --> 10:25.168
笙ｪWhen life resumes and settles the past笙ｪ

10:25.434 --> 10:29.254
笙ｪNo need to hide this flustered state笙ｪ

10:29.264 --> 10:32.894
笙ｪLet my candor redeem my recklessness笙ｪ

10:33.040 --> 10:37.200
笙ｪForgive myself笙ｪ

10:37.200 --> 10:38.768
笙ｪWhat kind of me笙ｪ

10:38.768 --> 10:40.967
笙ｪIs the best me?笙ｪ

10:40.967 --> 10:43.355
笙ｪWho defines it?笙ｪ

10:43.355 --> 10:44.674
(I have something for you too.)

10:45.435 --> 10:47.595
Your writing is full of emotion.

10:47.874 --> 10:48.955
It deeply moved me.

10:49.475 --> 10:50.274
I believe

10:51.955 --> 10:53.355
you love osmanthus jam very much.

10:54.378 --> 10:56.038
笙ｪIs the best me?笙ｪ

10:57.075 --> 10:58.595
After the nurse removed the needle,

10:58.914 --> 11:00.235
I feared you'd keep bleeding,

11:00.235 --> 11:01.595
so applied a band-aid.

11:02.506 --> 11:04.748
笙ｪIs the best me?笙ｪ

11:05.274 --> 11:06.315
So what's this?

11:07.514 --> 11:08.874
A reward for model behavior.

11:09.715 --> 11:10.315
Yan.

11:11.034 --> 11:11.794
Your kindness

11:13.634 --> 11:15.274
makes me want to give you every single

11:15.955 --> 11:16.715
good thing I see.

11:24.362 --> 11:31.856
(Wangda Road)

11:40.874 --> 11:42.554
(Looking at Shen Haoming now)

11:44.034 --> 11:45.355
(makes me recall a saying.)

11:47.794 --> 11:49.115
("Amidst the crowd.)

11:50.674 --> 11:51.835
(in the dark dusk,)

11:53.394 --> 11:54.514
(you are unrecognizable.)

11:56.034 --> 11:57.394
(And we won't meet again.")

12:04.595 --> 12:05.355
Have you decided?

12:12.955 --> 12:14.394
If you want a divorce,

12:16.235 --> 12:16.914
I'll agree.

12:18.715 --> 12:20.315
The New District project just launched.

12:21.315 --> 12:23.075
My career and family

12:23.955 --> 12:25.715
can't tolerate any disruptions.

12:26.955 --> 12:27.914
My upcoming schedule

12:28.195 --> 12:29.195
requires your presence.

12:29.914 --> 12:32.674
The New District project
launch ceremony is in two days.

12:33.075 --> 12:35.514
As my wife, you must attend.

12:36.955 --> 12:38.235
I don't want anyone

12:39.115 --> 12:41.595
to notice any changes between us.

12:53.554 --> 12:54.514
What if I say...

13:01.394 --> 13:02.355
I can't do it?

13:03.075 --> 13:05.835
You aren't officially part
of the News Department.

13:08.355 --> 13:09.595
I assume you don't want

13:09.595 --> 13:11.075
any mistakes in this process.

14:13.834 --> 14:19.856
(Huanhuan's Call)

14:32.195 --> 14:32.874
What's wrong?

14:33.595 --> 14:35.075
Yan, the editing

14:35.075 --> 14:36.715
for the last recording is all done.

14:36.914 --> 14:37.874
When will you come?

14:39.634 --> 14:40.274
Hello?

14:41.235 --> 14:42.514
Yan, are you listening?

14:43.514 --> 14:44.115
Hello?

14:47.715 --> 14:48.715
I am coming.

14:53.435 --> 14:55.754
That's all the news for today.

14:55.955 --> 14:57.034
Thank you for watching.

14:57.075 --> 14:58.394
See you.

14:59.634 --> 15:00.715
Great job. Wrap it up.

15:04.674 --> 15:05.235
Thank you.

15:07.794 --> 15:08.435
Xu Yan!

15:18.995 --> 15:19.955
Elegant and composed.

15:20.794 --> 15:21.554
Performed well.

15:21.955 --> 15:23.355
I knew I was right about you.

15:25.554 --> 15:26.355
In today's meeting,

15:27.154 --> 15:29.034
the leaders publicly praised you.

15:30.075 --> 15:33.355
They decided to have you host
the next Financial Forum.

15:34.274 --> 15:35.075
As you know,

15:35.274 --> 15:36.835
hosting the Financial Forum

15:37.034 --> 15:39.595
is the ultimate recognition
from the leaders.

15:42.914 --> 15:43.674
Thank you.

15:43.914 --> 15:45.115
Don't mention it.

15:45.715 --> 15:46.835
Get some rest.

15:47.154 --> 15:49.634
You're the backbone now.
Your health comes first.

15:50.075 --> 15:52.274
Poor rest affects your performance.

15:52.435 --> 15:53.874
Alright, I'm leaving.

15:58.674 --> 15:59.674
Goodbye, Ms. Xu.

16:00.715 --> 16:01.674
See you, Ms. Xu.

16:25.674 --> 16:27.554
(I can't refute)

16:29.315 --> 16:30.995
(anything that Shen Haoming said.)

16:34.514 --> 16:36.475
(I can't tell if my career's success)

16:38.235 --> 16:39.634
(is due to the support)

16:41.154 --> 16:42.355
(he provided to me.)

16:46.435 --> 16:47.595
(If I quit being)

16:47.595 --> 16:48.435
(as Mr. Shen's wife,)

16:51.315 --> 16:52.914
(will all this enthusiasm)

16:55.115 --> 16:56.154
(and smiles to me remain?)

17:51.146 --> 17:56.560
(Fang Lei's Call)

18:09.635 --> 18:10.354
You're back.

18:13.635 --> 18:14.915
Wash up. Dinner is ready.

18:16.314 --> 18:17.594
I made Western food for you.

18:17.995 --> 18:19.274
Haven't cooked this in ages.

18:21.074 --> 18:22.395
Wonder if I've gotten rusty.

18:36.915 --> 18:37.794
Get to the point.

18:40.114 --> 18:40.754
Haoming.

18:43.875 --> 18:45.034
I've been thinking a lot.

18:45.675 --> 18:47.235
You said I married you for wealth

18:48.594 --> 18:51.074
and Shen family's
resources and connections.

18:55.675 --> 18:57.395
As someone benefiting from all this,

18:58.435 --> 18:59.235
I admit

19:01.675 --> 19:03.475
everything I've achieved now

19:04.235 --> 19:05.435
can't be separated from you

19:06.834 --> 19:08.354
and the Shen family.

19:10.195 --> 19:11.514
So I won't deny

19:12.955 --> 19:14.274
I made the mistake first.

19:16.514 --> 19:18.354
I sincerely apologize to you.

19:20.955 --> 19:21.635
Besides,

19:23.834 --> 19:25.834
I'll genuinely accept Haochen

19:26.395 --> 19:27.875
just as you wanted.

19:28.794 --> 19:30.754
I'll properly take care of this family

19:32.034 --> 19:33.754
and manage my career well.

19:37.074 --> 19:38.435
I just want to tell you

19:39.955 --> 19:43.514
my love for you have been genuine,

19:46.034 --> 19:47.274
and I truly love you.

19:47.915 --> 19:50.235
After everything we've been through,

19:50.554 --> 19:51.834
how could all of it be fake?

19:54.875 --> 19:56.235
I know I was wrong.

19:59.235 --> 20:00.635
I truly understand now.

20:02.715 --> 20:04.274
Can we please...

20:07.274 --> 20:08.395
start over?

20:13.715 --> 20:14.715
I love you.

20:19.635 --> 20:20.834
I truly do.

20:48.675 --> 20:50.435
Just go for the fame or wealth.

20:52.675 --> 20:54.554
That way, I would think
you're being sincere.

21:00.754 --> 21:01.794
Like you said,

21:04.395 --> 21:05.594
we agreed

21:07.114 --> 21:08.274
whether at work

21:10.074 --> 21:11.074
or at home,

21:12.675 --> 21:14.155
we stick to our roles

21:14.915 --> 21:16.074
and maintain mutual benefit.

21:17.235 --> 21:18.395
Isn't this perfect?

21:18.995 --> 21:20.834
I recognize your value as a partner.

21:21.354 --> 21:23.635
After you've become
an official news anchor,

21:24.114 --> 21:25.794
I'll throw you a grand

21:26.514 --> 21:27.955
celebration party.

21:32.475 --> 21:33.754
Wish you have a success.

21:42.114 --> 21:44.274
So you still don't believe

21:46.834 --> 21:48.514
that I truly love you.

21:49.074 --> 21:49.715
Right.

21:54.314 --> 21:54.754
By the way,

21:55.754 --> 21:57.794
there's no need for such efforts.

21:59.955 --> 22:01.715
I admit your acting is superb,

22:02.715 --> 22:03.875
but you can only

22:05.235 --> 22:06.155
fool me once,

22:06.274 --> 22:07.794
not again.

22:13.395 --> 22:14.995
Delicious. Have a seat.

22:15.995 --> 22:16.635
Let's eat.

23:09.594 --> 23:10.635
(The current me,)

23:12.235 --> 23:14.435
(like the boy
who cried "the wolf is coming",)

23:16.155 --> 23:17.715
(told too many lies.)

23:19.395 --> 23:20.794
(So when I tell the truth,)

23:21.274 --> 23:22.675
(none will believe me.)

23:25.274 --> 23:26.794
(The sandcastle)

23:27.114 --> 23:28.354
(will eventually collapse.)

23:31.675 --> 23:33.195
(I deserve everything)

23:35.435 --> 23:36.955
(caused by my action.)

23:57.584 --> 23:59.792
(Jinda Group Huanyu International Project
Groundbreaking Ceremony)

24:02.675 --> 24:04.995
Ladies and gentlemen,

24:05.034 --> 24:05.955
good day.

24:06.155 --> 24:07.155
Welcome you

24:07.395 --> 24:10.715
to Jinda Group New District
real estate project's

24:10.834 --> 24:12.915
groundbreaking ceremony.

24:13.195 --> 24:15.114
Jinda Group has long upheld

24:15.235 --> 24:16.995
the concept of architecture in nature.

24:17.354 --> 24:19.034
This project

24:19.114 --> 24:21.274
must boost transformation

24:21.435 --> 24:22.514
of the New District

24:22.715 --> 24:26.354
and bring greater comfort and joy

24:26.395 --> 24:28.314
to all our citizens.

24:35.955 --> 24:37.435
Now, we'll proceed to

24:37.514 --> 24:38.794
(Guest)
today's groundbreaking ceremony,

24:38.955 --> 24:41.034
the most exciting moment.

24:41.235 --> 24:42.514
All dignitaries and guests,

24:42.554 --> 24:43.915
please come up here.

24:56.586 --> 24:58.128
(Groundbreaking)

25:01.875 --> 25:02.834
As hosts,

25:03.435 --> 25:03.995
smile.

25:05.274 --> 25:06.274
Take the golden shovels

25:06.475 --> 25:07.995
and break ground together.

25:09.794 --> 25:12.395
Let's count down together.

25:12.715 --> 25:17.715
Five, four, three, two, one!

25:22.675 --> 25:24.395
Congratulations to success

25:24.435 --> 25:26.314
of Jinda Group New District

25:26.395 --> 25:27.435
real estate project's

25:27.675 --> 25:29.475
groundbreaking ceremony!

25:31.435 --> 25:33.314
(Groundbreaking)
(We're reporters from Entertainment Frontline.)

25:33.594 --> 25:34.554
Mr. Shen.

25:34.675 --> 25:36.594
Regarding the New District project,

25:36.594 --> 25:37.995
you've put your wife's creative

25:38.155 --> 25:39.995
in the interior design concepts.

25:40.155 --> 25:41.635
Is that true?

25:42.155 --> 25:42.875
Right.

25:44.034 --> 25:46.114
Her dedication
and professional competence

25:46.235 --> 25:49.715
demonstrate remarkable wisdom.

25:51.155 --> 25:52.635
I deeply respect her capabilities

25:53.235 --> 25:55.314
and I'm always open to her insights.

25:56.354 --> 25:58.594
What's the secret

25:58.715 --> 25:59.635
to your strong bond?

25:59.715 --> 26:01.034
Can you share some tips?

26:10.435 --> 26:11.675
No secret at all.

26:12.594 --> 26:15.235
Luck comes first.

26:16.034 --> 26:16.794
Then,

26:17.195 --> 26:18.635
mutual admiration

26:18.955 --> 26:20.915
between spouses is crucial.

26:21.475 --> 26:22.915
I admire her capabilities so much.

26:23.395 --> 26:24.794
But what moves me most

26:25.314 --> 26:28.834
is that she can choose an easy job,

26:29.875 --> 26:31.435
even to be a housewife,

26:32.435 --> 26:33.675
yet she chose

26:34.034 --> 26:35.435
to pursue her childhood dreams

26:37.915 --> 26:39.195
without pause,

26:39.754 --> 26:41.314
striving tirelessly till today.

26:42.915 --> 26:45.594
This deeply moves me.

26:50.195 --> 26:51.675
So I want to cherish her more.

26:55.195 --> 26:58.235
How would you describe your husband now?

26:58.354 --> 27:01.235
What drew you to Mr. Shen?

27:01.274 --> 27:02.834
Could you share with us?

27:17.635 --> 27:18.635
My husband...

27:21.114 --> 27:23.074
is exceptional in every way,

27:24.594 --> 27:26.554
truly impeccable.

27:27.514 --> 27:29.675
So I'm lucky to meet him.

27:31.114 --> 27:32.794
But most importantly,

27:34.314 --> 27:35.274
he respects me,

27:35.882 --> 27:36.656
(Xu Yan's Profile)

27:38.435 --> 27:39.195
trusts me,

27:42.995 --> 27:43.715
and supports me.

27:44.995 --> 27:46.314
They say

27:46.794 --> 27:47.955
when choosing a husband,

27:48.594 --> 27:51.155
we should choose someone

27:51.235 --> 27:52.915
who truly cherishes us.

27:53.915 --> 27:55.195
My husband not only does this,

27:56.195 --> 27:56.955
but

27:58.514 --> 28:01.594
exceeds my expectations.

28:03.635 --> 28:04.715
I have to do better.

28:06.875 --> 28:07.554
Thank you.

28:07.635 --> 28:09.635
That's all for today's interview.

28:09.715 --> 28:12.354
Please prepare for
the group photo later.

28:12.395 --> 28:13.354
Thank you.

28:15.995 --> 28:16.915
Have a big smile.

28:18.195 --> 28:20.155
Here we go. Smile!

28:21.995 --> 28:22.594
Perfect.

28:35.235 --> 28:37.475
You performed terribly today.

28:38.435 --> 28:40.074
Especially during the press conference.

28:40.715 --> 28:42.715
You remained cold

28:43.514 --> 28:44.514
and unsmiling

28:45.594 --> 28:46.675
throughout.

28:48.034 --> 28:49.675
Tomorrow is a charity gala.

28:50.475 --> 28:52.715
I hope the same won't happen again.

28:54.114 --> 28:55.594
As long as you perform well,

28:56.715 --> 29:00.074
I guarantee you'll obtain the permanent

29:00.395 --> 29:01.554
news anchor position.

29:03.155 --> 29:04.034
Thank you, Mr. Shen.

29:20.970 --> 29:22.032
(WeChat Message)

29:31.690 --> 29:33.904
(Fang Lei: Can we meet?)

29:35.955 --> 29:36.915
(Can we meet?)

29:48.202 --> 29:50.544
(Han Weiping's Call)

29:55.915 --> 29:56.475
What's wrong?

29:57.395 --> 29:58.514
Fang Lei said

29:59.274 --> 30:00.915
she'd kill herself if you don't show up.

30:01.754 --> 30:02.314
Where is she?

30:02.834 --> 30:03.514
At her home.

30:04.635 --> 30:05.235
Got it.

30:09.314 --> 30:11.635
If I'm to keep playing
the role of a good wife,

30:12.995 --> 30:14.235
should I ask my husband

30:17.114 --> 30:18.915
about things like this?

30:19.754 --> 30:20.715
Unless I choose

30:21.794 --> 30:23.155
to tell you myself,

30:23.794 --> 30:25.715
don't ask any question.

30:37.395 --> 30:38.235
- Mr. Shen.
- Where is she?

30:38.435 --> 30:39.034
Living room.

30:43.155 --> 30:44.314
You finally showed up?

31:03.395 --> 31:04.635
You wanted to kill yourself?

31:05.114 --> 31:06.435
Go ahead. I'm waiting.

31:07.435 --> 31:08.395
Think I don't dare to?

31:10.235 --> 31:12.144
Didn't answer my calls
or reply to my messages,

31:13.074 --> 31:14.274
yet you showed up now?

31:16.155 --> 31:17.354
So you do get scared.

31:17.514 --> 31:18.915
You told Xu Yan about Haochen.

31:19.195 --> 31:21.955
You deserve to die.

31:33.554 --> 31:35.274
You still came here at this hour.

31:35.715 --> 31:36.915
You were already in bed,

31:37.155 --> 31:38.675
yet came to another woman.

31:38.794 --> 31:39.875
This just proves

31:39.915 --> 31:41.794
she only wants your wealth.

31:44.235 --> 31:46.274
You're off the New District project.

31:46.955 --> 31:47.794
What do you mean?

31:49.155 --> 31:50.915
Used me and then kicked me out?

31:51.675 --> 31:52.354
Never!

31:52.715 --> 31:53.675
I'm not leaving!

31:55.834 --> 31:57.675
Your bonus and compensation

31:58.475 --> 31:59.475
will be paid in full.

32:02.594 --> 32:04.794
Come to the office
and hand over your duties.

32:06.114 --> 32:07.354
I won't let you off!

32:07.834 --> 32:08.675
I'll kill myself!

32:08.754 --> 32:09.514
I'll kill myself!

32:09.554 --> 32:10.995
I'll! Really!

32:11.834 --> 32:13.314
Miss Fang, have a seat.

32:17.074 --> 32:18.554
Why are you still here?

32:19.435 --> 32:20.635
Get out now!

32:22.034 --> 32:23.675
I suggest you stop escalating it.

32:25.354 --> 32:26.675
I've accepted Mr. Shen's money,

32:27.195 --> 32:29.074
and our cooperation will only end

32:29.675 --> 32:31.475
until you stop making a mess.

32:34.594 --> 32:36.354
It turns out all these dramas

32:36.594 --> 32:37.395
get you nowhere.

32:37.915 --> 32:39.155
Why keep going

32:40.754 --> 32:42.034
and making me work overtime?

32:42.875 --> 32:43.314
Well,

32:44.034 --> 32:45.715
let me introduce you to some decent men.

32:46.114 --> 32:47.314
They are my former clients.

32:47.554 --> 32:48.995
Good guys, recently divorced.

32:49.074 --> 32:50.155
Good for you to kill time.

32:53.554 --> 32:54.834
Are you insane?

32:55.274 --> 32:56.955
Why always keep an eye on me?

32:57.554 --> 32:59.635
Studying homewreckers

32:59.635 --> 33:00.715
like you

33:01.074 --> 33:02.395
helps my work.

33:03.915 --> 33:04.715
Get lost!

33:07.402 --> 33:09.904
(Jingzhou Yuekang Hospital Outpatient)

33:15.034 --> 33:15.594
Nurse Liu,

33:16.475 --> 33:17.834
has Dr. Yu finished his surgery?

33:18.114 --> 33:19.074
Just finished,

33:19.114 --> 33:21.235
debriefing the family now.

33:22.074 --> 33:22.794
Thank you.

33:26.875 --> 33:27.475
Dr. Yu.

33:28.235 --> 33:30.314
Before the operation, you told me that

33:30.794 --> 33:31.794
the first operation

33:31.794 --> 33:33.235
would take three to four hours.

33:33.475 --> 33:34.354
But in reality,

33:34.875 --> 33:36.675
six full hours!

33:37.715 --> 33:39.074
My child is so young.

33:39.635 --> 33:41.475
He suffered so much!

33:41.715 --> 33:44.114
Please calm down.

33:44.715 --> 33:45.594
We inform families

33:45.594 --> 33:47.314
about estimated surgery duration.

33:47.834 --> 33:48.955
But we also clarify

33:49.274 --> 33:50.475
times vary between patients.

33:50.754 --> 33:52.074
It's only an estimate.

33:53.034 --> 33:54.155
Our priority is to ensure

33:54.155 --> 33:55.274
patient safety

33:55.635 --> 33:56.635
and prevent severe

33:56.635 --> 33:58.554
lung damage during procedures.

33:58.955 --> 34:00.034
It often takes three hours,

34:00.195 --> 34:01.074
six at maximum.

34:01.114 --> 34:02.155
This is normal.

34:02.314 --> 34:04.354
I wonder if it's because
of your incompetence.

34:04.635 --> 34:06.834
We're canceling the surgery.

34:09.514 --> 34:09.915
Go now.

34:10.795 --> 34:12.034
Get your supervisor now!

34:12.154 --> 34:14.355
I want a satisfied explanation today!

34:20.955 --> 34:22.154
Hello.

34:30.554 --> 34:32.714
You might not know Dr. Yu well.

34:33.074 --> 34:35.114
He's exceptionally skilled

34:35.315 --> 34:37.194
and dedicated.

34:37.554 --> 34:40.074
He sees 60 to 70 patients
daily in clinic.

34:40.315 --> 34:42.234
After that, he has
to go perform surgery.

34:42.475 --> 34:44.154
Standing over 10 hours.

34:44.395 --> 34:45.395
He can't even get meals,

34:45.475 --> 34:47.315
and sometimes can't even drink water.

34:47.674 --> 34:50.395
You could ask around to verify.

34:50.594 --> 34:51.835
Many of his patients

34:51.875 --> 34:53.554
speak highly of him.

34:54.154 --> 34:56.114
You brought me here

34:56.435 --> 34:57.315
just to tell me

34:57.315 --> 34:58.674
how hard-working Dr. Yu is?

34:59.074 --> 35:00.234
What does this have to do

35:00.234 --> 35:00.995
with my child?

35:01.114 --> 35:02.714
Well, I'm sorry.

35:02.755 --> 35:04.114
Not only that.

35:04.194 --> 35:06.074
I just wonder

35:06.194 --> 35:08.475
if you could show some understanding.

35:09.114 --> 35:10.034
Of course, I understand

35:10.034 --> 35:11.315
how you're feeling.

35:11.435 --> 35:12.435
When a child gets sick,

35:12.475 --> 35:13.835
no parent stays calm.

35:14.034 --> 35:15.875
And the expenses are huge.

35:16.114 --> 35:17.154
I just wonder

35:17.154 --> 35:18.475
if I can help ease

35:18.594 --> 35:19.955
your burden somehow

35:20.395 --> 35:21.875
and give you proper assurance.

35:22.315 --> 35:23.034
What?

35:23.234 --> 35:23.714
Yes.

35:24.475 --> 35:24.995
Here.

35:27.355 --> 35:28.154
Please take this.

35:34.795 --> 35:35.634
Who are you?

35:36.795 --> 35:38.355
What's this with you?

35:42.835 --> 35:45.034
I'm Dr. Yu's wife.

35:46.435 --> 35:47.074
Absurd!

35:47.875 --> 35:49.875
Bribing families to gain sympathy

35:50.154 --> 35:51.554
for medical staff?

35:51.674 --> 35:53.915
The complaint reached my office!

35:54.795 --> 35:55.795
What?

35:59.514 --> 36:00.795
Who bribed the families?

36:00.835 --> 36:01.795
Your wife.

36:03.594 --> 36:04.275
Yu Yiming.

36:04.435 --> 36:05.915
When did you get married?

36:06.114 --> 36:07.114
Why didn't I know it?

36:07.634 --> 36:08.554
My wife?

36:09.594 --> 36:10.674
I'm single.

36:11.275 --> 36:11.674
Wait,

36:11.674 --> 36:12.714
are you mistaken?

36:13.475 --> 36:15.194
The girl who keeps visiting you.

36:17.275 --> 36:18.194
I'm sorry.

36:18.435 --> 36:19.315
So sorry

36:19.435 --> 36:20.475
I caused you trouble.

36:20.955 --> 36:22.034
I gave her money

36:22.034 --> 36:24.594
just to help relieve
her financial pressure,

36:24.795 --> 36:26.634
so you can do your surgery smoothly.

36:26.915 --> 36:28.594
I didn't think that much.

36:29.154 --> 36:30.315
I truly realize my mistake.

36:30.315 --> 36:31.835
I'm sorry. So sorry.

36:31.955 --> 36:33.714
I was so careless.

36:33.955 --> 36:34.755
This is my fault.

36:34.835 --> 36:35.355
I swear

36:35.395 --> 36:36.594
it'll never happen again.

36:39.194 --> 36:41.154
Did the hospital punish you?

36:44.234 --> 36:46.074
I'll go explain it.

36:47.315 --> 36:49.355
I'll apologize to the family personally,

36:49.514 --> 36:51.114
and then clarify with hospital admin

36:51.154 --> 36:52.674
that you had nothing to do with this.

36:52.835 --> 36:53.995
It's all my fault.

36:54.275 --> 36:55.114
I'll go do it.

36:55.355 --> 36:56.275
Want to apologize?

37:00.514 --> 37:01.114
Come with me.

37:02.795 --> 37:03.755
Hold on.

37:04.594 --> 37:05.355
Take them.

37:07.594 --> 37:10.937
(I Miss You in China)

37:14.634 --> 37:16.194
Is this enough?

37:18.875 --> 37:19.915
You bought me ice cream.

37:20.355 --> 37:21.034
I forgive you.

37:24.355 --> 37:25.355
Not just that,

37:26.435 --> 37:27.234
I should thank you.

37:29.034 --> 37:31.475
After our communication
and explanations,

37:31.594 --> 37:32.514
she understands

37:32.514 --> 37:33.674
the surgery's complexity

37:33.915 --> 37:35.920
and multiple procedures needed.

37:35.920 --> 37:38.395
She's willing to cooperate with us
to continue the treatment.

37:38.395 --> 37:40.034
Regarding your wife's actions,

37:40.315 --> 37:41.275
she forgave her.

37:41.995 --> 37:42.955
Yes! Fantastic!

37:52.594 --> 37:53.234
I'm sorry.

37:54.154 --> 37:54.755
What?

37:56.795 --> 37:59.154
She kept asking me

37:59.554 --> 38:00.955
about our relationship.

38:01.315 --> 38:02.435
I didn't know how to answer

38:02.435 --> 38:04.315
and said I'm your wife.

38:05.074 --> 38:05.955
Sorry.

38:28.435 --> 38:29.955
- Hello.
- Hello.

38:30.154 --> 38:30.674
Hello.

38:31.514 --> 38:32.234
Long time no see.

38:32.795 --> 38:34.034
Today makes a difference.

38:34.955 --> 38:35.554
See you.

38:37.674 --> 38:38.355
Lei.

38:43.554 --> 38:45.395
- You're here too.
- Yes.

38:46.714 --> 38:47.714
Where are you sitting?

38:48.315 --> 38:49.234
Over there.

38:51.674 --> 38:53.234
So far away?

38:54.634 --> 38:56.154
Can you even see the auction items?

38:57.475 --> 38:57.915
Come here.

39:01.554 --> 39:02.234
Sit here.

39:03.875 --> 39:04.915
Have you been tired?

39:05.355 --> 39:06.154
Not really.

39:06.315 --> 39:07.074
Exhausted?

39:07.435 --> 39:08.234
No.

39:09.714 --> 39:10.475
Good then.

39:10.594 --> 39:11.475
Working all day,

39:11.835 --> 39:13.114
you must take care.

39:18.355 --> 39:18.875
Lei.

39:41.915 --> 39:42.475
Lei.

39:44.074 --> 39:45.315
I just noticed

39:45.435 --> 39:46.755
your complexion looks dull.

39:46.875 --> 39:47.915
Been staying up late?

39:48.674 --> 39:50.154
No, my complexion has been great.

39:50.594 --> 39:51.315
Good then.

39:53.995 --> 39:55.275
I wanted to tell you

39:56.355 --> 39:57.594
I've been really busy,

39:58.194 --> 39:59.755
working overtime.

40:00.475 --> 40:01.915
If you are available,

40:02.034 --> 40:03.074
could you help

40:03.074 --> 40:04.355
look after Haoming more?

40:07.315 --> 40:08.835
I know you two

40:08.875 --> 40:10.074
studied abroad together,

40:10.315 --> 40:11.315
so you know him well.

40:12.074 --> 40:12.714
Fang Lei.

40:14.395 --> 40:15.955
The investors for Qingwan Project,

40:16.795 --> 40:18.755
Mr. Qiu and his wife are at table six.

40:19.234 --> 40:20.355
Go chat with them.

40:21.995 --> 40:22.634
Sure.

40:28.514 --> 40:30.194
Don't tell her to do so.

40:31.795 --> 40:32.995
She's seated here.

40:33.154 --> 40:34.674
Just give her a break.

40:38.755 --> 40:41.395
They can always chat another time.

40:42.355 --> 40:44.435
Listen to me, stay here.

40:47.835 --> 40:49.795
Look, it's starting.

40:58.915 --> 41:00.275
Everyone,

41:00.315 --> 41:01.475
welcome to

41:01.475 --> 41:04.514
the 2024 Celebrity Entrepreneurs
Charity Gala.

41:04.915 --> 41:07.114
Charity Spirit, Forever Love.

41:07.234 --> 41:08.915
All proceeds from tonight's auction

41:09.074 --> 41:12.114
will support Hope Primary Schools.

41:12.194 --> 41:13.634
Let's give warm applause

41:13.674 --> 41:14.875
to wish tonight's auction

41:15.034 --> 41:16.395
a complete success.

41:19.755 --> 41:20.795
Thank you.

41:21.114 --> 41:22.755
Now I'll present

41:22.835 --> 41:24.194
our first auction item.

41:25.875 --> 41:27.475
(Angel's Tear Diamond Ring)
This ring features

41:27.514 --> 41:29.475
a 7.09-carat royal blue

41:29.514 --> 41:33.194
sapphire from Kashmir.

41:33.234 --> 41:35.275
The color is fancy black blue.

41:35.514 --> 41:37.514
Clarity is VS1.

41:37.714 --> 41:39.234
It's like an angel's tear.

41:39.315 --> 41:40.234
Not just jewelry,

41:40.355 --> 41:42.154
but a spiritual symbol

41:42.395 --> 41:43.875
and an emblem of love.

41:44.154 --> 41:45.915
We'll start bidding

41:46.074 --> 41:48.275
at 500,000 RMB.

41:48.514 --> 41:50.154
Bidding begins now.

41:50.475 --> 41:51.355
600,000.

41:51.435 --> 41:52.034
600,000.

41:52.074 --> 41:53.355
600,000 from left.

41:54.194 --> 41:54.995
650,000.

41:55.154 --> 41:57.114
650,000 from right.

41:57.395 --> 41:58.234
650,000.

41:58.395 --> 42:00.514
Any higher bids?

42:00.755 --> 42:01.435
700,000.

42:01.475 --> 42:02.154
700,000.

42:02.395 --> 42:04.234
700,000 from behind.

42:04.275 --> 42:05.395
Current bid 700,000.

42:05.395 --> 42:07.995
Any higher bids than 700,000?

42:08.194 --> 42:09.755
Last call!

42:09.875 --> 42:10.514
700,000.

42:11.634 --> 42:12.315
One million.

42:12.995 --> 42:14.074
One million.

42:14.554 --> 42:15.514
One million.

42:17.234 --> 42:18.995
Any higher bids?

42:18.995 --> 42:20.435
Bid stands at one million.

42:20.714 --> 42:21.315
One million.

42:21.514 --> 42:22.795
Anyone else?

42:23.074 --> 42:23.755
1.2 million.

42:23.995 --> 42:25.315
1.2 million!

42:25.435 --> 42:27.074
Any higher bids?

42:27.795 --> 42:28.995
1.4 million!

42:29.114 --> 42:30.234
1.4 million!

42:30.275 --> 42:31.835
Back row bids 1.4 million.

42:31.875 --> 42:33.275
1.6 million.

42:33.594 --> 42:35.554
1.6 million.

42:36.194 --> 42:38.154
Left side offers 1.6 million.

42:38.275 --> 42:39.995
Any more bids?

42:41.315 --> 42:42.915
1.6 million.

42:43.234 --> 42:44.395
First call.

42:44.955 --> 42:46.355
1.6 million.

42:46.755 --> 42:48.194
Second call.

42:55.514 --> 42:56.355
Three million.

